    Class
    Description
    Classroom
    The Classroom class models an online classroom.
    DatabaseChangeListener
    Handles changes with Firebase database reference.
    DatabaseModifier
    Creates and interacts with Firebase; handles actions used to submit, fetch, and access essays, submissions, and other parts Allows the user to be able to add and set values inside the Database.
    Rubric
    Models an assignment for a classroom.
    RubricRow
    Models a row of a rubric with a grading criteria.
    Student
    The Student class models a student in the online classroom.
    Submission
    The Submission class models a submission that a student makes to the teacher.
    Teacher
    Models a teacher user that will be part of a classroom.
    User
    The User class is a template for the users that will be using the Database.
